.hero.is-medium.is-primary.is-fullwidth
  %canvas#canvas{:height=>"400px"}
  .hero-body.has-text-centered
    %h1.title Guthrie Schoolar
    %h3.subtitle Full Stack Web and Software Developer
  .hero-footer
    .container
      %nav.tabs.is-fullwidth.is-boxed
        %ul
          %li#education-button.is-active
            %a{:onclick=>"openContent('education')"}
              %i.fa.fa-graduation-cap.space
              %span.button-content Education
          %li#projects-button
            %a{:onclick=>"openContent('projects')"}
              %i.fa.fa-code.space
              %span.button-content Projects
          %li#about-button
            %a{:onclick=>"openContent('about')"}
              %i.fa.fa-user.space
              %span.button-content About
.container
  .section.content
    .container{:style=>"max-width:950px"}
      .section.tab-content#education{:style=>"display: block"}
        %h1 Education
        %p I'm a senior at the University of North Texas getting a B.S. in Computer Science and a certificate in Game Programming. I'm always looking for ways to better myself and learn new technologies!
        %br/
        .columns
          .column
            %h3 Coursework
            %ul
              %li C++ and Object Oriented Programming
              %li Software Engineering
              %li Systems Architecture and Operating Systems
              %li Artificial Intelligence
              %li Data Structures and Algorithms
              %li UX Design
              %li Game programming
              %li Game Math and Physics
          .column
            %h3 Languages and Libraries
            %ul
              %li C/C++
              %ul
                %li Unreal 4
                %li Boost
                %li Network and Socket Programming
              %li Ruby on Rails
              %li Lua
              %ul
                %li LÖVE2D
                %li Corona SDK
              %li HTML/CSS/JS
              %ul
                %li JQuery
                %li NodeJS
                %li ReactJS
                %li Sass
                %li Canvas programming
              %li Python
              %li Assembly, VHDL
      .section.tab-content#projects
        %h1.title Projects
        %h4.subtitle
          Check out my
          %a.has-text-primary{:href=>"http://github.com/thegoobs", :target=>"_blank"}
            %strong.has-text-primary Github
          to see what I've been working on.
        .columns.is-desktop.is-multiline
          .column
            .card
              .card-image
                %figure.image.is-4by2
                  %img{:src=>"images/maddness_featured.png"}
              .card-content
                %p.title Maddness
                %p.subtitle Available now on Google Play and the App Store!
                %p
                  Download for
                  %a.has-text-primary{:href=>"https://goo.gl/Sr7Wfm", :target=>"_blank"}
                    %strong iOS
                  and
                  %a.has-text-primary{:href=>"https://goo.gl/gY37za", :target=>"_blank"}
                    %strong Android.
                %p
                  Built in Lua with Corona SDK. Clear number tiles in
                  a 5x5 grid by adding them up, and destroy them if the
                  sum is zero.
          .column
            .card
              .card-image
                %figure.image.is-4by2
                  %img{:src=>"images/lasersharks.jpg"}
              .card-content
                %p.title Laser Sharks
                %p.subtitle Unreal 4 project for a Game Programming course at UNT.
                %p
                  Created water biome environment, animated rigged mesh, implemented basic game
                  structure for two game modes, and implemented AI behavior trees. (Github repo unavailable)
          .column
            .card
              .card-image
                %figure.image.is-4by2
                  %img{:src=>"images/yinyang.png"}
              .card-content
                %p.title Yin-Yang
                %p.subtitle C++ 2D platformer made with DirectX and Visual Studio.
                %p
                  Lead programmer, implemented game mechanics, character control, Enemy AI,
                  Game states and structure, animation and graphics.

      .section.tab-content#about
        %h1.title About
        %h4.subtitle Who I am, and how to get in touch.
        .columns
          .column.has-text-centered
            %img{:src=>"images/self-portrait.jpg", :width=>"300px", :style=>"border-radius: 100%; margin-top: 25px;"}
            %br/
            %br/
            .has-text-centered
              %a.button.is-primary{:href=>"guthrie_schoolar_resume.pdf", :target=>"_blank", :style=>"margin-bottom: 12px"}
                %i.fa.fa-file-text.space
                Resume
              .button.is-primary{:onclick=>"revealEmail()"}
                %i.fa.fa-envelope.space
                Email Me
              %br/
              %br/
              %p.subtitle.has-text-centered#info-content
          .column
            %p

              <strong>I'm currently looking for entry level Software and Web Dev jobs and internships.</strong>
              %br/
              %br/
              Aside from academics, I work as a Resident Assistant at Bruce Hall, one of the dorms at UNT. I have served in many
              other leadership positions on campus, including being an 
              Orientation Leader and the Vice President of a student Organization that connected programmers and designers together to make websites and other neat projects.
              %br/
              %br/
              I'm originally from Austin Tx, which basically means I'm a cowboy and I bleed queso.
              %br/
              My hobbies include playing video games and
              making music with my brothers.
              %br/
              The woman in the picture with me is my wonderful girlfriend,
              Briana. She has supported me unconditionally through everything
              and I cannot thank her enough for all of her love.

